  icons/interlux-icons/hardware/gpu.svg
  icons/interlux-icons/hardware/usb-drive.svg
  icons/interlux-icons/peripherals/mouse.svg
    Uncredited public-domain icons.

See icons/README.md for the human-readable attribution table.
